1. Find the Google Font on fontsource.org

2. Type "npm install @fontsource/<font-name>

3. In import section of astro file, type "import '@fontsource/<font-name>;

4. Go to tailwind.config.cjs and an entry in the fontFamily section. Write 
the name of the Tailwind style you will use and paste the CSS rule from 
Google Fonts inside a [], like this:

theme: {
	fontFamily:{
		<name>: [<css rule>],
	},	
},
